title: Serpent Ancestor
summary: Serpent Ancestor Manhua English An old snake accidentally ate an elixir in a village, gaining intelligence and embarking on the path of cultivation. The life of a snake, though only for a brief decade, is lived without the fear of time, seizing every moment. This is the story of an old snake who became an immortal. Snake Immortal: Devouring the Immortal Emperor at the Beginning, The Tale of the Old Snake’s Cultivation to Immortality, 老蛇修仙传 The Legend of the Old Snake’s Immortal Cultivation Snake Immortal: The Tale of a Snake’s Cultivation to Immortality Tale of the Old Snake’s Immortal Cultivation
